com.kuka.roboticsAPI.safetyModel

Class ControllerSafetyState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.safetyModel.ControllerSafetyState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISafetyState

    public final class ControllerSafetyState
extends Object
implements ISafetyState
    Class to get the state of controller safety signals. Safety states are returned as consistent, immutable snapshots at a single point in time. For an update, a new request needs to be sent, or a listener for controller state changes needs to be implemented.
